rios", "summary": "Abstract: Target speech extraction (TSE) has achieved strong performance in relatively simple conditions such as one-speaker-plus-noise and two-speaker mixtures, but its performance remains unsatisfactory in noisy multi-speaker scenarios. To address this issue, we introduce a lightweight speech enha...", "link": "https://arxiv.org/abs/2508.19583", "source": "arXiv Audio & Speech", "image": "https://arxiv.org/html/2508.19583v1/fig1.png", "score": 10}]}